{"tid":1681132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開始清算警隊了","createTime":"2019-10-29T08:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T09:12:38.000Z","uid":326123,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"55055242f02d63efaa9c9f5c27ea5edb9b5d152b","tid":1681132,"uid":326123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />林鄭：不容忍違法暴力，包括警察<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人權民主法案大機會通過，警犬高層想調職<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中央放風要林鄭下台<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />劉業成將離任<br />\n<br />\n林鄭同劉業成都講過「一日有佢係度，都唔會成立獨立調查委員會」<br />\n宜家兩條友都要走，咁即係好快就會成立獨立調查委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信宜家警隊己經度緊要交咩人出嚟祭旗<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">清算要開始了</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c7ecf1db4d6a753486b8bafa7cc02661bb1b4a","tid":1681132,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:30:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"c2778879205ead1b0ad06aae63987647ef2484ff","tid":1681132,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警</strong>得罪中央犯死罪</span>，三萬科士<span style=\"color: red;\">大禍臨頭</span>！<br />\n+ <span style=\"color: gold;\">送條妙計<strong>俾阿Sir解圍</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我早幾日出咗呢個post講阿Sir已經死到臨頭，<br />\n早幾日明報放風話中共要從嚴治警、政府放風話要獨立調查時間一致。<br />\n<br />\n我呢個post俾咗條計三萬科士一條生路，<span style=\"color: red;\">再唔行動就瓜硬</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671833\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671833</a>"},{"pid":"63c200244a015c2d5a85b51bffcd95371b5ea526","tid":1681132,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:31:51.000Z","msg":"送俾啊Sir一招不死必勝法，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">立即行動</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">拯救三萬警察<strong>避免獨立調查</strong></span>！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1674172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1674172</a>"},{"pid":"be7ffa4b7fa826d64ce4c60e7cffa3dbb5c4a40f","tid":1681132,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2778879205ead1b0ad06aae63987647ef2484ff","tid":1681132,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警</strong>得罪中央犯死罪</span>，三萬科士<span style=\"color: red;\">大禍臨頭</span>！<br />\n+ <span style=\"color: gold;\">送條妙計<strong>俾阿Sir解圍</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我早幾日出咗呢個post講阿Sir已經死到臨頭，<br />\n早幾日明報放風話中共要從嚴治警、政府放風話要獨立調查時間一致。<br />\n<br />\n我呢個post俾咗條計三萬科士一條生路，<span style=\"color: red;\">再唔行動就瓜硬</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671833\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671833</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:33:04.000Z","msg":"<em>「從嚴治警」是習近平今年5月初，在全國公安工作會議提出的。除了首要的「對黨忠誠」的政治要求外，習近平強調公安要「服務人民、執法公正、紀律嚴明」，從而鍛造一支讓黨中央放心、人民群眾滿意的高素質過硬公安隊伍。</em>"},{"pid":"2a241b4b342026b4f27d74c213a890d091807021","tid":1681132,"uid":326123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:33:36.000Z","msg":"睇你班condom仔點死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42aa8fab0985ad992fb7ddd608243dd573a16f45","tid":1681132,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be7ffa4b7fa826d64ce4c60e7cffa3d